name: Sterling Silver Hand Bracelet with Swarovski Accents - Sterling Silver Hand Chain
description:
Delicate and beautiful sterling silver hand chain. Accented with Swarovski Crystals for a very soft, dainty look. Every component is sterling silver and put together with love and care. 

Made to fit a size 7 finger. Length from middle knuckle to wrist is 3.5 inches and a 7 inch wrist. If you believe you need a different size please contact me. Bracelet is extendable by 1 inch on the wrist (6.5-7.5 inches).

Ships from the US in a jewelry gift box and bow. 

I ship via USPS and orders within the US are usually received within 3 business days. Outside the US is approximately 4-7 business days. Some countries can take up to 8 weeks for delivery.

name: Set of Three Sterling Silver Knuckle Rings
description:
Set of Three Sterling Silver Filled Knuckle Rings. Sweet and simple little rings. These rings do form a full circle and are closed at the back. Slim stackable rings. You can order them in 2 or 3 different sizes. 

When choosing your sizes you want to go about 2.5-3 sizes smaller than the ring size of the finger you intend to wear it on.
